{"type": "article", "id": 15083, "title": "调色桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-18T07:26:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135741leKzax7hrnEstXYp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计品牌 &amp;tradition 邀请西班牙设计师 Jaime Hayon 和意大利设计师 Luca Nichetto 做了一组调色桌，采用三块在材质、形状和颜色上都不一样的材料组合，然后高低不一排列起来。比如抛光的大理石搭配水曲柳和铜，再用黑色亚光处理的焊接钢管支撑，达到一种巧妙的平衡。设计师称灵感来源于 lexander Calder 的象征性的雕塑，也想以此表现多样化的生活。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261424174MAKO3aBUxnq9XTv.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142418i31NWjIGxQdwHTrZ.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78239609\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142418VniwCkc85l1UhQOY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}